        <p>NDS is an exclusive and authorized applicator of all Steriltex products. The disinfectant products are
        hospital grade, CDC, and EPA- Registered and N Listed approved cleaners and disinfectants. Products are
        engineered to combat 99.5 % of all viruses, bacteria, and pathogens including SARS-CoV -2, the cause of
